STAR WARS OPTION SWITCH DOCUMENTATION	17-MAY-83					( NOTE:     ***    indicates the manufacturer's recomended options )----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------OPTION SWITCH BANK 1  ( Board Location 10C )	Switches	1   &   2 :	STARTING SHIELDS			ON	ON		6			OFF	ON		7		***	ON	OFF		8			OFF	OFF		9	Switches	3   &   4 :	PLAY DIFICULTY			ON	ON	    Easy		***	OFF	ON	  Moderate			ON	OFF	    Hard			OFF	OFF	  Hardest	Switches	5   &   6 :	BONUS SHIELDS FOR DESTROYING DEATH STAR							( Shield strength will not go higher than STARTING SHIELDS level )			ON	ON		0		***	OFF	ON		1			ON	OFF		2			OFF	OFF		3	Switch		7 :		MUSIC IN ATTRACT MODE		***	ON		   Every 7 minutes during attract mode one of the stored pieces of music will be heard			OFF		   No music during attract	Switch		8 :		FREEZE MODE/STOP ACTION			ON		   Freezes the action on the screen, the left fire button advances the action by one frame					   ( Interrupt driven graphics are not stopped ie. flash colors, fireballs, splash )		***	OFF		   Normal game play mode----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
OPTION SWITCH BANK 2	( Board Location 10E/F )	Switches	1   &   2 :	COIN VALUE			ON	ON	Free Play			OFF	ON	2 Credits		***	ON	OFF	1 Credit			OFF	OFF	1/2 Credit	Switches	3 :		LEFT COIN MECHANISM MULTIPLIER ( Possible Half-Dollar Mech )		***	ON		    1 Coin			OFF		    2 Coins	Switches	4   &   5 :	RIGHT COIN MECHANISM MULTIPLIER ( Possible Dollar Mech )		***	ON	ON	    1 Coin			OFF	ON	    4 Coins			ON	OFF	    5 Coins			OFF	OFF	    6 Coins	Switches	6   &   7   &   8 :	BONUS COIN ADDER		***	ON	ON	ON	    None			OFF	ON	ON	  2 Gives 1			ON	OFF	ON	  4 Gives 1			OFF	OFF	ON	  4 Gives 2			ON	ON	OFF	  5 Gives 1			OFF	ON	OFF	  3 Gives 1			ON	OFF	OFF	    None			OFF	OFF	OFF	    None----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
OPTION SWITCH BANK 3 ( Board Location 11L )	Switch		1 :		ELECTROMECHANICAL COIN COUNTER TIE-IN		***	ON		   Outputs of coin counter driver 1 and 2 tied together ( for 1 counter )			OFF		   Outputs of coin counter driver 1 and 2 separate ( for 2 counters )	Switch		2   &   3   &   4 :	UNUSED----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------